      "title": "Tensor product multiplicities and convex polytopes in partition space",
      "abstract": "Westudy multiplicities in the decompositionof tensorproduct of two lire- ducible finite dimensionalmodules over a semisimple complex Lie algebra. A con- jectural expressionfor such multiplicity is given asthe numberof integralpoints of a certain convexpolytope. Wediscusssome specialcases,corollariesandconfirmations of the conjecture."
